snippet.title: Kitty Letter - A free game from the creators of Exploding Kittens
snippet.description:
In this free mobile game from the creators of  Exploding Kittens, players wield a magical vortex to unscramble words.  These words transform into ARMIES that attack your opponent.  The game also features an extensive single-player campaign with comics by The Oatmeal.

Download it now:
App Store: https://apps.apple.com/app/id1510395712
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.ExplodingKittensInc.KittyLetter
